      <title>[인사] 고용노동부 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2025/01/06/Y7JUR5447NFSXMJEN52M5DVV24/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2025/01/06/Y7JUR5447NFSXMJEN52M5DVV24/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
